List of notable or famous field hockey players from the Netherlands, with bios and photos, including the top field hockey players born in the Netherlands and even some popular field hockey players who immigrated to the Netherlands. If you're trying to find out the names of famous Dutch field hockey players then this list is the perfect resource for you. These field hockey players are among the most prominent in their field, and information about each well-known field hockey player from the Netherlands is included when available.

The list you're viewing is made up of people like Marcel Balkestein and Tim Jenniskens.

This historic field hockey players from the Netherlands list can help answer the questions "Who are some Dutch field hockey players of note?" and "Who are the most famous field hockey players from the Netherlands?" These prominent field hockey players of the Netherlands may or may not be currently alive, but what they all have in common is that they're all respected Dutch field hockey players.

Use this list of renowned Dutch field hockey players to discover some new field hockey players that you aren't familiar with. Don't forget to share this list by clicking one of the social media icons at the top or bottom of the page. {#nodes}
